title: Dustin Lynch And Parents On His Childhood + 5 True Things About Bobby That Sound Like A Lie + Lunchbox Hits The Streets For Drunk Trivia
itunes:title: Dustin Lynch And Parents On His Childhood + 5 True Things About Bobby That Sound Like A Lie + Lunchbox Hits The Streets For Drunk Trivia
description:
Dustin Lynch brings his parents in with him for our Friday Morning Conversation. We learn all about what he was like as a kid, his hometown of Tullahoma and the secret to being married for 40 years. Mike D reads a list about Bobby on things that sound fake, but are actually true about him. Lunchbox goes out on the streets to ask people who have had a little too much to drink easy trivia questions!
